edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來可以合法泊第二三線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他司機泊埋去應該會比潮聯攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f95ddb2688e6fd27d3f86ac19d3dbf58b1c5e78","tid":353910,"uid":30457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"車主們夠唔夠疆玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f20797b1dddf9902eb7cb01f878335f166d62df","tid":353910,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"觀繞，東區走廊，屯公二三線......"},{"pid":"067e0b3c9e904118739f23f6a772517a5242f160","tid":353910,"uid":48582,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"原來成條彌敦道都係車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7cc5240071138b74c6bcf8be831a75bff1a3ee","tid":353910,"uid":121982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"車聚啦喂"},{"pid":"4651104e8919286a1caf37bcf6ab124c94897051","tid":353910,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來成條彌敦道都係車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拍到去尖咁碼頭都仲有得泊佢條第2線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ddd47a2a88541d6cf4dd2d9597ea0d4a750d31","tid":353910,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來成條彌敦道都係車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拍到去尖<span style=\"color: red;\">咀</span>碼頭都仲有得泊佢條第2線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0ef4ec887a8de1c0f717dcb080d01c703bf6561","tid":353910,"uid":122534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快速公路快線無禁止停止牌同埋無雙黃，原來一直有咁多車位唔知道，難怪要嚴厲執法啦</blockquote><br />\n除非中途壞車或遇有緊急事故，否則不得在快速公路任何一處停車或泊車。如遇到上述事故，必須亮起危險警告燈。可能的話，駛離行車道，並在路旁帶上停車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係都揀市中心停喇,公路停車上落,路邊都一係好遠先有出口一係鐵絲網擺托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ae53767bc0758f9539de48a2b8598ab3797e0f","tid":353910,"uid":83910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"原來當日佔旺果陣成埋貨van塞住條亞皆老街係合法架？"},{"pid":"8b6654af111284b9f637802929ae45980824c87b","tid":353910,"uid":35351,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"I-cable記者加油"},{"pid":"ca23c4b6d54496b5cd2fc7bcf2712282a6c0520e","tid":353910,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"最好就係一早泊哂D私家車係二三線 睇潮聯班小巴佬會做D乜行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886ccdb74f35b210cccfc13bdae3d90b4a4e4726","tid":353910,"uid":93784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"BTW 有線記者好波!"},{"pid":"ae01e6c68a6d224837b32299632ad2a6600b512d","tid":353910,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"如果有幾十人不停打去投訴會點?"},{"pid":"eb68cff4606d678f7630ce14f9cacee49b6016e3","tid":353910,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有幾十人不停打去投訴會點?</blockquote><br />\n尋釁滋事"},{"pid":"7a0924e7f9e185d2d70ed05d1d1d475b7a92b979","tid":353910,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"有線新聞加油！"},{"pid":"99890ddfd9771749affdf9a14836dc9f86fd2130","tid":353910,"uid":71441,"like":0,"di